OL,3,CSix charged over rioting at hotel
OL,4,Chousing asylum seekers
OL,6,FSix more people have been charged over
OL,7,Frioting at a hotel housing asylum
OL,8,Fseekers in Rotherham.
OL,10,FHundreds of people gathered at the
OL,11,FHoliday Inn Express in Wath-upon-
OL,12,FDearne, in Rotherham, on Sunday.
OL,14,FObjects were thrown at police, leaving
OL,15,Fat least 12 injured, and some of the
OL,16,Fhotel's windows were smashed in what
OL,17,FSouth Yorkshire Police called a
OL,18,F"disgusting display of thuggery".
