OL,3,CSix charged over rioting at hotel
OL,4,Chousing asylum seekers
OL,6,FA group of rioters got into the hotel
OL,7,Fand a bin was pushed against the wall
OL,8,Fand set alight.
OL,10,FOn Tuesday, police said three men had
OL,11,Fbeen charged with violent disorder:
OL,12,FLee Crisp, 42, of Mount Road,
OL,13,FGrimethorpe, Christopher Rodgers, 38,
OL,14,Fof Millmoor Road, Barnsley and Liam
OL,15,FGrey, 20, of Randerson Drive. Two boys
OL,16,Faged 16 and 17, who cannot be named
OL,17,Fbecause of their age, are facing the
OL,18,Fsame charge.
