OL,3,CSix charged over rioting at hotel
OL,4,Chousing asylum seekers
OL,6,FJoshua Simpson, 26, of Sherbrook
OL,7,FStreet, Lincoln, is charged with
OL,8,Fviolent disorder and assault of an
OL,9,Femergency worker.
OL,11,FAll were due to appear in Sheffield
OL,12,FMagistrates' Court on Tuesday.
OL,14,FCurtis Coulson, 30, of Water Slacks
OL,15,FRoad, Sheffield, appeared in court on
OL,16,FMonday charged with affray in relation
OL,17,Fto a separate incident in Sheffield.
OL,19,FHe has been remanded into custody
OL,20,Funtil his next court appearance on
OL,21,FFriday, 9 August.
